WEBVTT

00:07.640 --> 00:08.960
‎SAY NO TO PIRACY, SUPPORT ORIGINALS

01:37.040 --> 01:42.920
‎ADAPTED FROM XI XING’S NOVEL
<i>‎QUEEN CHU</i>‎ ON QIDIAN.COM

01:47.440 --> 01:49.720
I'll kill you, you traitor!

01:49.800 --> 01:50.920
You deserve to die!

01:51.000 --> 01:52.720
Traitor!

01:52.800 --> 01:55.360
-Traitor!
-Go die!

01:55.440 --> 01:57.160
You deserve to die!

01:57.240 --> 01:58.760
-Shameless!
-You don't deserve to live on.

01:58.840 --> 02:01.160
-I'll make you pay!
-Die!

02:02.320 --> 02:03.600
You should pay!

02:03.680 --> 02:04.840
Die!

02:07.360 --> 02:08.199
Drop dead!

02:09.880 --> 02:12.400
-You took General Chu's life!
-Die!

02:12.480 --> 02:14.040
-General Chu was such an honorable man.
-Traitor!

02:14.120 --> 02:15.680
-You don't deserve to live.
-Go die!

02:15.760 --> 02:17.840
-Go to hell!
-Beat you to death!

02:17.920 --> 02:21.120
-I'll kill you!
-You treacherous parasite!

03:13.200 --> 03:15.120
<i>You ferocious little thing.</i>

03:15.200 --> 03:16.080
<i>You've got a vicious bite.</i>

03:16.920 --> 03:18.160
<i>I hurt your men.</i>

03:18.880 --> 03:19.720
<i>Just go ahead and kill me.</i>

03:21.400 --> 03:22.880
<i>You wish to die?</i>

03:35.280 --> 03:36.680
Do you know why?

03:37.360 --> 03:40.600
Because deep down,
you still cling to life.

03:52.760 --> 03:55.520
Since you're not going to die today,
you're coming with me.

04:00.360 --> 04:01.440
Kill him!

04:07.040 --> 04:09.240
Give way! Stand clear!

04:09.320 --> 04:10.360
Move aside!

04:10.440 --> 04:11.960
-Clear out, all of you!
-Make way!

04:12.960 --> 04:16.160
Whatever Xie Yanlai's crimes may be,
he will face a military tribunal.

04:16.240 --> 04:18.040
None of you may take justice
into your own hands!

04:22.800 --> 04:24.000
On your feet.

04:26.440 --> 04:27.960
At that time,

04:28.040 --> 04:30.880
we knew that medicine
was meant to save the General.

04:30.960 --> 04:33.640
Nobody could have foreseen
that it would end up like this.

04:33.720 --> 04:35.320
The court even honored your service

04:35.400 --> 04:37.360
and rewarded you
for the Northern Desert campaign.

04:37.440 --> 04:38.440
Why are you groveling?

04:38.520 --> 04:40.360
Who are you trying to atone to?

04:41.160 --> 04:42.320
Honored?

04:46.840 --> 04:48.280
That honor was bought
with the General's life.

04:48.360 --> 04:50.880
We had no better choice back then.

04:54.160 --> 04:56.040
You…

05:00.000 --> 05:01.200
Goodness.

05:05.160 --> 05:06.560
A mistake is a mistake.

05:07.520 --> 05:08.760
There is no excuse for it.

05:48.320 --> 05:51.480
Since when does Yunzhong Prefecture
allow vigilante justice?

06:04.200 --> 06:05.280
CAPITAL

06:25.920 --> 06:26.840
Your Highness, please discern the truth!

06:26.920 --> 06:31.120
General Chu died a senseless death,
and we cannot stomach this injustice!

06:31.200 --> 06:33.080
He's a monster in human skin!

06:33.160 --> 06:36.440
If he is innocent of General Chu's murder,
why submit to punishment so readily?

06:36.520 --> 06:38.840
Did any of you actually witness
him commit the murder?

06:43.520 --> 06:45.320
THE GREAT BORDER GATE

06:46.640 --> 06:47.600
Xie Yanlai.

06:48.880 --> 06:52.640
Before the people of Yunzhong Prefecture,
I will ask you one last time.

06:54.600 --> 06:56.040
Did you truly intend

06:57.560 --> 06:58.960
to harm my father?

07:06.760 --> 07:08.920
Your Highness,
you mustn't believe a word he says.

07:09.000 --> 07:10.480
He's of the Xie Family!

07:13.640 --> 07:15.720
He entered my father's service at 16.

07:16.480 --> 07:18.520
Xie Yanlai is first a soldier
of the Chu Army,

07:18.600 --> 07:19.720
only then, a member of the Xie Family.

07:22.200 --> 07:25.480
If you wonder how my father died,

07:27.680 --> 07:29.240
I shall lay bare the truth now.

07:30.200 --> 07:31.160
Army Physician!

07:32.000 --> 07:35.520
The poison that struck the General
is known as the Bloodburn Pill,

07:35.600 --> 07:38.120
refined from several lethal toxins.

07:39.000 --> 07:43.160
In a short span,
it forces the blood to race

07:43.240 --> 07:45.480
and causes a violent surge
of physical strength.

07:45.560 --> 07:49.240
It can even grant a dying man
a final, fleeting burst of vitality.

07:49.960 --> 07:52.440
Three years ago,
at the Battle of the Frontier River,

07:52.520 --> 07:54.480
General Chu was struck
by a poisoned arrow.

07:55.000 --> 07:56.920
The Army Physician was entirely helpless.

07:57.000 --> 07:59.720
I watched as the General
coughed up blood relentlessly.

07:59.800 --> 08:01.680
It was Jiu's pill

08:01.760 --> 08:04.880
that dragged the General back
from the very brink of death.

08:04.960 --> 08:05.800
No way!

08:05.880 --> 08:08.280
We believed that medicine
was his last hope.

08:08.360 --> 08:10.080
But who could have guessed

08:10.600 --> 08:11.920
it would only defer the General's demise
at a terrible cost?

08:12.920 --> 08:14.920
Yet, if we hadn't used it that day,

08:15.520 --> 08:20.040
the General
would have perished on the spot.

08:22.920 --> 08:24.480
Did we truly misjudge him?

08:24.560 --> 08:26.520
-He didn't do it?
-Really?

08:26.600 --> 08:27.760
In the 14th year of Tianshu,

08:28.800 --> 08:30.360
Jiu first joined Yunzhong Prefecture.

08:31.760 --> 08:32.880
While on patrol,

08:33.720 --> 08:35.520
he discovered a Northern Desert scout
infiltrating our frontier.

08:36.679 --> 08:40.440
Though only a boy of 16,
he fought them off at all costs,

08:41.039 --> 08:44.159
sustaining multiple stab wounds,
one just half a cun from his heart.

08:44.960 --> 08:46.080
In the 15th year of Tianshu,

08:47.240 --> 08:50.560
when the Northern Desert troops
raided a frontier village,

08:53.040 --> 08:54.560
General Chu led the counterattack.

08:55.280 --> 08:59.080
Jiu took a spear strike
meant for the General on his shoulders,

08:59.840 --> 09:01.800
shielding the entire village.

09:02.640 --> 09:04.840
In the 16th year of Tianshu,
when the enemy struck again,

09:05.440 --> 09:07.320
he defended the frontier river
with the General.

09:07.840 --> 09:10.120
He took two hits amidst a hail of arrows,

09:10.760 --> 09:12.040
but managed to chop down the drawbridge,

09:12.120 --> 09:16.240
halting the enemy's advance
and sparing the State of Chu

09:16.320 --> 09:17.800
from total devastation.

09:18.520 --> 09:20.080
And during the recent battle of Wangcheng,

09:20.800 --> 09:22.080
he infiltrated the enemy camp alone

09:22.720 --> 09:24.280
to sabotage their provisions
and water supplies,

09:24.360 --> 09:26.560
nearly losing his life in the fray.

09:28.040 --> 09:32.120
Would a man like this
truly harm his own commander?

09:32.200 --> 09:33.040
-Indeed.
-Right…

09:33.120 --> 09:37.440
Every scar on Jiu's body was earned
while shielding you all.

09:37.520 --> 09:40.360
If you want to take his life,
look at those wounds

09:40.440 --> 09:42.720
and ask yourselves
if your consciences can bear it.

09:45.240 --> 09:47.760
Are we to kill a man
who saved General Chu,

09:48.360 --> 09:51.680
Yunzhong Prefecture, and the State of Chu,

09:52.200 --> 09:53.920
just on a rumor?

09:54.720 --> 09:55.600
Back then,

09:56.400 --> 10:00.200
Fu Jiu snuck into
a Northern Desert camp to save us

10:00.840 --> 10:03.920
and took the branding for us
when he was discovered.

10:04.640 --> 10:05.760
Back at the frontier river,

10:06.280 --> 10:08.720
I was about to be crushed
under the enemy cavalry.

10:09.240 --> 10:10.440
It was Fu Jiu who dragged me back.

10:10.520 --> 10:13.520
I saw him risk his life for the General.

10:13.600 --> 10:16.240
I refuse to believe
a man like that could turn traitor.

10:16.920 --> 10:20.040
Look at all his scars.

10:20.560 --> 10:22.280
Fighting the Northern Desert troops

10:23.000 --> 10:25.280
must have been a constant dance
with death.

10:25.960 --> 10:28.760
Looking at what he's endured,
I shall never believe…

11:23.160 --> 11:24.000
Thank you.

11:24.880 --> 11:28.200
I was just telling…
the people what really happened.

11:29.880 --> 11:31.120
This incident did not happen by chance.

11:32.240 --> 11:33.760
Someone must be pulling the strings.

11:35.480 --> 11:36.320
It is all my fault.

11:39.640 --> 11:41.520
If he hadn't taken the medicine
I provided…

11:43.000 --> 11:45.800
Zhao. I know you hate me.

11:47.120 --> 11:48.440
You have every right to.

11:49.880 --> 11:50.840
I did hate you once.

11:52.680 --> 11:53.680
But I realize

11:55.160 --> 11:57.600
that you were merely a convenient outlet
for my grief and fury.

11:59.360 --> 12:00.960
I felt so utterly powerless,

12:01.960 --> 12:06.040
with no one to hold accountable
or to blame.

12:06.960 --> 12:11.600
After all, this was my father's choice.

12:12.560 --> 12:15.680
He chose to die
on the battlefield as a commander,

12:16.760 --> 12:17.840
claiming one final victory

12:17.920 --> 12:20.040
over his lifelong nemesis,
the Northern Desert King.

12:21.400 --> 12:25.160
And I was there,
fighting right alongside him.

12:26.520 --> 12:28.200
He lived his final moments

12:29.040 --> 12:32.720
to the fullest, with no regrets.

12:37.760 --> 12:39.800
I have no right to blame you.

12:41.560 --> 12:42.480
If anything…

12:45.720 --> 12:47.200
I ought to thank you.

12:57.160 --> 12:58.960
The General dictated this,

12:59.800 --> 13:02.480
ordered me to record it,
and bring it to you.

13:18.080 --> 13:21.360
<i>Zhao, to read these words</i>
<i>is to meet again.</i>

13:22.520 --> 13:24.640
<i>Last night, I saw you in my dreams.</i>

13:25.160 --> 13:28.360
<i>You were still that young girl,</i>
<i>spurring your horse away from home.</i>

13:29.360 --> 13:31.360
I reached out to hold you back,

13:31.880 --> 13:35.400
but my hand caught nothing
but drifting sand.

13:36.440 --> 13:40.600
Only now do I realize
that 19 years on the battlefield

13:41.400 --> 13:42.800
have long stripped me

13:44.240 --> 13:46.120
of the right to be your father.

13:47.640 --> 13:49.200
<i>That year, you asked me in tears</i>

13:50.680 --> 13:54.600
<i>why I kept you confined</i>
<i>to the desolate desert.</i>

13:55.480 --> 13:59.120
<i>I mistook it for youthful rebellion.</i>

13:59.200 --> 14:01.480
<i>I never understood</i>
<i>that what you yearned for</i>

14:02.440 --> 14:04.640
<i>was never the Capital's splendor,</i>

14:05.680 --> 14:09.600
but merely a light
left burning beneath the eaves

14:10.920 --> 14:12.320
to welcome you home.

14:13.680 --> 14:18.120
<i>I've heard that the noble ladies</i>
<i>of the Capital are prideful and harsh.</i>

14:19.160 --> 14:24.680
<i>I cannot bear to think how much scorn</i>
<i>you've endured among them.</i>

14:25.560 --> 14:27.280
<i>Every time the thought crosses my mind,</i>

14:28.480 --> 14:30.120
<i>it tears at my very soul.</i>

14:31.560 --> 14:33.320
For 19 years,

14:34.480 --> 14:37.080
I was not there to guide your early steps,

14:38.200 --> 14:41.520
<i>nor to instruct you in the classics.</i>

14:42.960 --> 14:46.400
<i>I am consumed by remorse.</i>

14:47.160 --> 14:48.920
<i>If life could start again,</i>

14:49.560 --> 14:53.440
<i>you would not be called</i>
<i>the daughter of a hero,</i>

14:54.320 --> 14:56.440
<i>but of Chu Ling, of mine.</i>

14:57.400 --> 14:58.280
<i>Might that be enough?</i>

15:06.280 --> 15:08.600
General. I'll fetch the Army Physician.

15:08.680 --> 15:09.920
Finish it.

15:13.000 --> 15:16.840
I have spent half my life in the saddle.

15:18.760 --> 15:20.240
I've failed none

15:22.120 --> 15:23.760
but my wife and daughter.

15:25.040 --> 15:29.640
Now, I ask for nothing
but your forgiveness.

15:30.640 --> 15:33.840
<i>Though tomorrow I may fall</i>
<i>on the battlefield,</i>

15:34.520 --> 15:36.440
<i>I shall embrace death with a smile.</i>

15:37.800 --> 15:38.920
<i>Zhao,</i>

15:40.360 --> 15:42.400
<i>water flows forward, never to return.</i>

15:43.040 --> 15:44.880
Do not look back.

15:47.120 --> 15:48.760
Keep moving forward.

15:50.440 --> 15:54.840
<i>From your father, Chu Ling,</i>
<i>in his final hour.</i>

16:00.000 --> 16:00.840
Stop.

16:10.800 --> 16:11.840
Jiu.

16:14.720 --> 16:18.720
Why didn't he tell me these things sooner?

16:20.800 --> 16:25.680
If he had just spoken up earlier,
I might have had time to make amends.

16:26.840 --> 16:28.320
And my mother.

16:29.240 --> 16:34.960
She will never hear
what I longed to tell her.

16:37.520 --> 16:38.480
I know.

16:40.520 --> 16:41.720
I truly understand.

16:41.800 --> 16:43.360
The last words

16:44.520 --> 16:50.040
of my father were that war is too cruel.

16:52.200 --> 16:54.280
He asked when it would finally end.

16:56.240 --> 16:59.080
My father gave his life for this victory.

17:00.640 --> 17:02.960
But if the flames of war
are never quenched,

17:04.280 --> 17:06.079
what meaning did their sacrifice have?

17:17.119 --> 17:18.319
I will ensure

17:20.319 --> 17:21.800
the State of Chu

17:22.640 --> 17:24.839
never again paves the road
to peace with blood.

17:27.640 --> 17:29.920
I will make sure the children of this land

17:31.560 --> 17:35.680
never lose their parents
to the scourge of war.

18:07.600 --> 18:09.800
Playing the saint again, are you?

18:09.880 --> 18:13.600
You claim you can shield an entire city,
but can you even protect yourself?

18:13.680 --> 18:15.880
What good is a second chance at life?

18:16.800 --> 18:19.320
You still had to watch your father die

18:19.920 --> 18:21.840
and your mother meet her bitter end.

18:23.000 --> 18:24.400
But neither of them

18:26.480 --> 18:28.560
regretted the choices they made.

18:28.640 --> 18:29.880
Self-delusion, nothing more.

18:30.520 --> 18:33.560
Lest you forget,
your enemies remain untouched.

18:34.840 --> 18:36.360
Not just Xiao Xun,

18:37.080 --> 18:39.400
but the Northern Desert
that destroyed your parents.

18:40.280 --> 18:41.600
If I were you,

18:41.680 --> 18:43.520
I would march the army
against the Northern Desert now

18:43.600 --> 18:45.280
and drown them in a reckoning of blood.

18:46.320 --> 18:47.240
No.

18:49.720 --> 18:51.800
The frontier troops
have bled far too much.

18:51.880 --> 18:52.840
And what of it?

18:52.920 --> 18:54.640
Glory is built upon bones.

18:54.720 --> 18:56.600
War demands sacrifice.

18:56.680 --> 18:58.680
Their blood means nothing to you.

18:59.600 --> 19:01.200
The army is yours to wield.

19:01.880 --> 19:02.880
Say the word,

19:02.960 --> 19:06.480
and they shall obey
and bleed for your cause.

19:07.360 --> 19:11.400
Don't you want to avenge your parents
upon the Northern Desert King?

19:13.480 --> 19:15.200
Mercy is weakness.

19:16.040 --> 19:18.520
Only slaughter endures.

19:33.840 --> 19:36.600
The pond needs cleaning.

19:41.800 --> 19:43.080
What a plump chicken.

19:46.360 --> 19:47.480
Look at this one.

19:47.560 --> 19:48.720
Give it to me.

19:48.800 --> 19:50.400
-Let's go.
-Come and have a look!

19:50.480 --> 19:52.440
-Miss Chu.
-Miss Chu.

19:52.520 --> 19:55.240
-Miss Chu.
-It's rare to see you out so early.

19:55.320 --> 19:56.160
What are you looking for?

19:56.240 --> 19:57.200
You're welcome to choose from my shop.

19:59.640 --> 20:00.600
Take your time.

20:00.680 --> 20:01.920
Do come by when you're free.

20:03.800 --> 20:06.160
Sweet and crisp pears.

20:07.760 --> 20:10.280
Miss Chu. Miss Chu.

20:10.360 --> 20:12.960
Miss Chu. These pears were freshly picked.

20:13.560 --> 20:14.760
Please, try some.

20:14.840 --> 20:17.440
No, thank you. You should keep them.

20:17.520 --> 20:18.600
The harvest has been exceptional
this year.

20:18.680 --> 20:20.640
Just take them
as a share of our good fortune.

20:20.720 --> 20:22.440
When General Chu was still with us,

20:23.160 --> 20:24.360
he always loved our pears.

20:25.520 --> 20:26.720
-Please, take it.
-I'll take it.

20:28.000 --> 20:30.680
Alright. Miss Chu,
I'll get back to work then.

20:39.080 --> 20:40.480
-This gadget
-Come and see.

20:40.560 --> 20:42.840
-can also be used to catch rats.
-Fresh flatbread.

20:42.920 --> 20:44.000
Is that so?

20:44.800 --> 20:46.960
Take a look. Fresh flatbread.

20:47.800 --> 20:50.360
Hot flatbread.
Get your fresh flatbread here.

20:52.200 --> 20:55.240
These flatbreads are meant for sale,
so stop gorging yourself on them.

20:56.000 --> 20:58.920
Are you some kind of gluttonous beast?

20:59.440 --> 21:00.760
I'm giving you a beating right now.

21:00.840 --> 21:03.200
KEEN, DETERMINED, SCHOLARLY, AND STRATEGIC

21:07.720 --> 21:08.600
Stop right there.

21:11.040 --> 21:12.360
Have you been out brawling again?

21:14.160 --> 21:15.000
Did you lose?

21:15.520 --> 21:16.360
I won.

21:16.440 --> 21:18.120
It was three against one,

21:18.200 --> 21:20.160
and I left every single one of them
eating dirt.

21:20.240 --> 21:22.200
You're covered in bruises.

21:22.280 --> 21:23.120
What is there to be proud of?

21:23.800 --> 21:25.640
They were calling me a motherless child.

21:29.440 --> 21:31.880
And so, you used your fists
to shut them up?

21:31.960 --> 21:32.960
Why did I allow you
to practice martial arts

21:33.040 --> 21:34.360
in the first place?

21:35.200 --> 21:36.080
To beat people up.

21:37.840 --> 21:40.040
To protect the defenseless.

21:40.120 --> 21:45.640
Your fists should be aimed at villains,
not at children your own age,

21:46.240 --> 21:47.520
and certainly never at your own people.

21:52.320 --> 21:53.200
What's on your mind?

21:54.080 --> 21:55.400
I was just thinking

21:57.520 --> 21:58.520
about something my father said.

22:00.280 --> 22:01.320
See?

22:02.520 --> 22:07.120
My father didn't give his life
for these cold city walls,

22:08.280 --> 22:09.480
but for the laughter…

22:09.560 --> 22:10.400
Two <i>wen</i> will be enough.

22:10.480 --> 22:11.320
…and for the

22:12.120 --> 22:13.400
hustle and bustle of daily lives.

22:14.840 --> 22:18.640
Seemingly ordinary
and insignificant though they be,

22:18.720 --> 22:22.200
yet these things are held dear
above all price in every heart.

22:22.960 --> 22:25.360
I seek no grand vision
of a tranquil realm.

22:25.960 --> 22:28.480
I ask only that the hearth-smoke
of Yunzhong Prefecture rises each day

22:29.400 --> 22:31.640
and that mothers may stand at their gates

22:32.240 --> 22:34.240
awaiting their children
to come home for dinner.

22:35.080 --> 22:37.800
The worst thing
these people should have to worry about

22:37.880 --> 22:39.920
is if the price of rice has gone up
by a few <i>wen</i> tomorrow.

22:40.800 --> 22:41.640
That is enough.

22:42.760 --> 22:48.040
We drift through our days,
sunrise to sunset, unaware

22:48.920 --> 22:50.280
that this life we take for granted

22:50.880 --> 22:52.680
is the very thing others would kneel
and pray for, yet never get.

22:52.760 --> 22:56.680
Fresh pears! Come and have a look!

22:56.760 --> 22:58.280
Maybe in the farmer's eye, the pears

23:00.760 --> 23:02.640
taste sweeter than they did last year,

23:04.440 --> 23:05.280
right?

23:08.280 --> 23:09.240
Jiu.

23:10.800 --> 23:13.640
Please guard Yunzhong Prefecture
in my father's stead.

23:14.240 --> 23:15.800
Become the sharpest blade

23:16.480 --> 23:18.080
in the State of Chu,
just as Chu Ling once was.

23:19.760 --> 23:20.640
I will.

23:24.160 --> 23:26.040
Your Highness, there is stirring
from the Northern Desert.

23:26.120 --> 23:28.240
An enemy scouting team
is probing our frontier.

23:33.400 --> 23:34.560
What's the situation?

23:34.640 --> 23:36.880
The enemy's vanguard launched
a surprise raid on our fortress.

23:36.960 --> 23:38.760
Our left flank has deployed
to encircle and eliminate them.

23:39.600 --> 23:40.760
Your Highness, please rest assured.

23:40.840 --> 23:44.440
We can split our forces
and strike the Chi'na Unit's main army.

23:46.080 --> 23:47.000
Wait.

23:47.080 --> 23:48.360
The scout actually pinpointed

23:48.440 --> 23:50.280
the exact movements
of Chi'na Unit's main force.

23:52.920 --> 23:53.760
During the last battle,

23:54.400 --> 23:56.840
the Northern Desert King's main troops
retreated at least 80 li.

23:57.960 --> 24:01.680
Their elite forces
are still stationed near Yingzui Cliff.

24:01.760 --> 24:03.280
It is physically impossible

24:04.560 --> 24:06.240
for the Chi'na Unit
to appear here within a mere two days.

24:07.640 --> 24:10.320
This surprise raid is a tactical trap.

24:11.000 --> 24:12.560
Then our left flank
is walking into a disaster.

24:12.640 --> 24:13.600
More than just a disaster.

24:14.200 --> 24:18.600
If this truly is an ambush,
our left flank will be entirely wiped out.

24:20.480 --> 24:23.560
We must crush this offensive
before it can even develop.

24:24.280 --> 24:26.840
But our reserves can only hold one front.

24:26.920 --> 24:28.440
If we divert troops
to reinforce the flank,

24:28.520 --> 24:31.080
our main defensive line
will be left completely exposed.

24:31.760 --> 24:33.560
-Then we'll borrow forces.
-From whom?

24:34.240 --> 24:35.200
The Cangmu Stronghold.

24:36.440 --> 24:37.920
Defeating Tie Ying at Cangmu Forest

24:38.000 --> 24:40.880
came down to their familiarity
with woodland combat,

24:40.960 --> 24:42.040
an advantage our troops could not match.

24:42.760 --> 24:44.800
If we can harness their strength
to coordinate with our forces,

24:44.880 --> 24:46.200
the victory will be ours.

24:47.000 --> 24:49.920
But the Cangmu Stronghold is…

24:50.000 --> 24:51.240
My father has just passed away.

24:51.320 --> 24:53.360
Neither the army's morale
nor the people's trust must waver.

24:53.440 --> 24:54.280
Should we fall in this battle,

24:54.960 --> 24:56.360
the Northern Desert
will strike with all their might.

24:57.240 --> 24:58.960
Mr. Zhong, we have no retreat.

24:59.840 --> 25:01.560
Very well. We will proceed as you suggest.

25:17.440 --> 25:18.280
Rest assured.

25:20.120 --> 25:23.720
I will fight to my last breath
to secure victory.

25:26.600 --> 25:27.480
Xie Yanlai, take your orders.

25:30.760 --> 25:31.720
Yes, Your Highness.

25:32.400 --> 25:33.320
Go…

25:34.800 --> 25:35.640
and stay alive.

25:52.240 --> 25:53.360
This is no military order.

25:55.360 --> 25:56.360
This is my order.

26:02.600 --> 26:03.560
Yes, Your Highness.

26:48.360 --> 26:49.240
Move out!

27:32.280 --> 27:35.040
XIE RESIDENCE

27:35.120 --> 27:37.760
Deng Yi actually had the audacity
to investigate our old estate in Gaoyang.

27:38.280 --> 27:39.760
The news about Xie Yanlai
and the Bloodburn Pill

27:39.840 --> 27:41.120
must have been leaked by him as well.

27:41.880 --> 27:45.800
Deng Yi is actually targeting my clan.

27:47.160 --> 27:48.520
He is truly ruthless,

27:49.560 --> 27:52.720
bent on wiping out my entire clan.

27:53.240 --> 27:55.240
Deng Yi is a man of profound calculation.

27:55.840 --> 27:57.000
If not for your benevolence,

27:57.080 --> 27:58.320
how could he have been allowed
to live until this day?

27:59.600 --> 28:01.520
He was the Grand Mentor
appointed by the late Emperor

28:02.680 --> 28:04.400
and holds the position of Regent,

28:05.520 --> 28:07.360
so he cannot be easily disposed of.

28:08.080 --> 28:10.160
Moreover, he still has
Xiao Xun as a fallback plan.

28:11.240 --> 28:12.920
Since Xiao suffered
a setback in Wangcheng,

28:13.000 --> 28:14.680
he will certainly not let the matter rest.

28:17.440 --> 28:18.400
A fallback plan?

28:19.000 --> 28:20.280
He calculated everything
in the battle of Wangcheng,

28:20.360 --> 28:21.560
yet his entire plan fell through.

28:22.880 --> 28:24.280
He can barely save himself now.

28:24.360 --> 28:28.680
Although the Northern Desert was defeated,
this war was like a massive earthquake.

28:29.520 --> 28:32.480
The real aftershocks
are just about to begin.

28:33.760 --> 28:36.160
Xiao Xun will definitely bide his time
to make a move.

28:38.200 --> 28:40.520
Keep a close eye on Xiaonan Prefecture.

28:42.040 --> 28:43.000
Yes.

28:58.480 --> 29:00.280
CHU

29:12.840 --> 29:14.080
Zhao,

29:14.160 --> 29:16.720
however anxious you are,
you must eat something.

29:18.080 --> 29:20.720
Mr. Zhong, I have no appetite.

29:24.880 --> 29:26.240
Victory!

29:26.840 --> 29:27.920
Victory!

29:28.440 --> 29:29.960
Your Highness,
Assistant General Xie has won!

29:30.040 --> 29:31.200
He routed the enemy's vanguard

29:31.280 --> 29:32.480
and even captured the Northern Desert
King's son-in-law alive!

29:34.720 --> 29:39.040
-Victory!
-Victory!

29:39.120 --> 29:41.120
Our troops' morale is now secure.

29:41.640 --> 29:43.200
General Zhong, you can rest assured now.

29:43.920 --> 29:46.280
With Her Highness here,
a great victory is all but certain.

29:46.360 --> 29:49.160
Quick! Report our triumph
to the Capital at once!

29:49.680 --> 29:51.200
Let everyone know

29:51.280 --> 29:54.680
that even though
Guard General Chu Ling is gone,

29:54.760 --> 29:56.200
the frontier still achieves
great victories,

29:56.280 --> 29:58.200
and the state remains secure.

29:58.280 --> 29:59.320
Yes!

30:02.600 --> 30:06.280
-Victory!
-Victory!

30:16.120 --> 30:16.960
There is a city ahead.

30:17.560 --> 30:18.680
Go in and announce the victory.

30:19.560 --> 30:22.040
Have the yamen
spread the news across the region!

30:27.720 --> 30:29.080
The Northern Desert has returned,

30:29.160 --> 30:30.280
their cavalry has broken
through Bailang Pass,

30:30.880 --> 30:32.640
and Yunzhong Prefecture
shall fall within three days.

30:32.720 --> 30:34.120
The Northern Desert army marches
straight for the Capital!

30:34.200 --> 30:35.840
The Northern Desert army marches
straight for the Capital!

30:35.920 --> 30:37.960
The Northern Desert army marches
straight for the Capital!

30:42.040 --> 30:44.640
Your Highness, there is one thing
I do not understand.

30:45.920 --> 30:46.800
Speak.

30:48.120 --> 30:50.600
We are already at odds
with the Northern Desert,

30:51.120 --> 30:53.920
so why do you still believe
they will help us?

30:54.520 --> 30:55.840
You are wrong, Tie Ying.

30:57.240 --> 31:02.160
Since the battle of Wangcheng,
I have expected nothing more from them.

31:03.400 --> 31:05.320
To share dominion?

31:06.480 --> 31:08.600
It is nothing but their idle dream.

31:09.200 --> 31:12.200
The war with the Northern Desert
has shaken the land,

31:12.720 --> 31:14.200
and the aftershocks are bound to follow.

31:14.280 --> 31:16.240
With Chu Ling gone,

31:17.160 --> 31:19.520
the Northern Desert King
will seize the moment to invade.

31:20.480 --> 31:23.960
I will use them
to shackle Yunzhong Prefecture.

31:24.560 --> 31:27.160
So what if Chu Zhao wins the battle?

31:28.040 --> 31:31.040
As long as the news
never reaches the Capital,

31:31.800 --> 31:33.480
this victory never happened.

31:34.080 --> 31:35.280
We've killed the dispatch riders

31:35.800 --> 31:37.320
and turned news of victory
into news of defeat.

31:39.400 --> 31:42.000
Once the Capital descends into panic,

31:43.160 --> 31:46.640
be it victory or defeat,

31:46.720 --> 31:50.120
I'll have my pretext
to march under the banner

31:50.200 --> 31:51.560
of protecting the Capital.

31:51.640 --> 31:53.200
And when that moment comes,

31:54.200 --> 31:58.720
it will be time for someone else
to sit on the throne.

32:00.320 --> 32:01.160
Your Highness is wise.

32:20.400 --> 32:23.880
What task is this that has distressed
Your Majesty so?

32:24.400 --> 32:26.120
How could any task trouble me?

32:26.640 --> 32:28.400
I am writing a letter to Zhao.

32:29.440 --> 32:33.000
The loss of parents is something
no words can console.

32:33.520 --> 32:34.360
I know.

32:38.920 --> 32:40.520
Your Majesty, Mr. Xie
requests an audience.

32:41.120 --> 32:41.960
It is so late.

32:42.040 --> 32:43.360
Tell Mr. Xie that I have retired
for the night.

32:43.440 --> 32:44.400
But Mr. Xie…

32:44.480 --> 32:46.400
I have an urgent matter
to discuss with His Majesty.

32:47.120 --> 32:48.000
You may withdraw.

32:49.080 --> 32:49.920
You're dismissed.

33:03.040 --> 33:05.360
Uncle, what is it
that you wish to tell me?

33:05.960 --> 33:08.360
The dispatch riders reported
that the Northern Desert had returned.

33:08.440 --> 33:10.000
They raided at midnight,
and our frontier troops fell.

33:10.800 --> 33:13.040
They have routed Yunzhong Prefecture
and are heading straight for the Capital.

33:13.640 --> 33:14.520
Upon hearing the news,
the Prince of Xiaonan Prefecture

33:14.600 --> 33:15.960
assembled 50,000 troops

33:16.040 --> 33:17.560
and is now 800 li away from the Capital.

33:23.680 --> 33:24.600
Yu,

33:26.080 --> 33:27.000
do not be afraid.

33:27.880 --> 33:30.960
The news may not necessarily be true.

33:31.560 --> 33:33.040
It might just be a ploy to create panic,

33:33.560 --> 33:36.000
making it convenient for the Prince
to lead his troops into the Capital

33:36.080 --> 33:37.480
under the pretext of defending the city.

33:38.080 --> 33:40.280
Are they planning to rebel?

33:40.920 --> 33:43.200
From the very moment
the Prince left the Capital,

33:43.720 --> 33:45.080
he has always harbored treasonous intent.

33:45.680 --> 33:48.480
This matter is of grave importance,
which is why I came in the dead of night.

33:49.240 --> 33:54.040
We must first agree on how to respond
during tomorrow's court session.

33:56.400 --> 33:57.480
<i>An urgent dispatch has arrived.</i>

33:57.560 --> 33:59.640
The Northern Desert has returned.

33:59.720 --> 34:01.600
Their cavalry has broken
through Bailang Pass,

34:01.680 --> 34:03.880
and Yunzhong will fall within three days.

34:03.960 --> 34:05.520
The enemy is pressing toward the Capital.

34:08.719 --> 34:11.760
With Chu Ling dead,
the frontier is indeed…

34:11.840 --> 34:13.960
The Grand Princess is a woman after all,

34:14.760 --> 34:17.480
so how could we truly expect her
to defend the frontier?

34:18.080 --> 34:20.000
Xiao Xun, heir to the Lord of Xiaonan,

34:20.080 --> 34:22.920
has led 50,000 troops
to defend the Capital

34:23.679 --> 34:25.360
and is only a few days' journey away.

34:27.040 --> 34:29.800
I petition Your Majesty
to open the city gates

34:29.880 --> 34:34.280
and let them in to defend the Capital
to ensure its peace.

34:34.360 --> 34:35.199
‎DILIGENT AND VIRTUOUS

34:35.280 --> 34:38.400
The Prince of Xiaonan
commands 50,000 troops,

34:39.040 --> 34:41.800
the Capital another 50,000,

34:41.880 --> 34:45.080
and with forces
from other prefectures combined,

34:45.159 --> 34:49.239
we have more than enough to hold
against the Northern Desert troops.

34:49.960 --> 34:53.679
There is indeed less reason to panic.

34:56.120 --> 34:56.960
Ignorant.

34:57.880 --> 35:00.080
A prince granted a fiefdom

35:00.680 --> 35:02.160
may collect its taxes
and live off its revenues,

35:02.680 --> 35:04.040
but holds no authority over troops.

35:04.720 --> 35:08.640
Even their guard
is capped at a fixed number.

35:09.320 --> 35:11.040
Where did he find 50,000 troops?

35:11.640 --> 35:14.320
In my view,
the Prince of Xiaonan Prefecture

35:14.400 --> 35:16.960
uses the defense of the Capital
as a pretext

35:17.040 --> 35:18.800
to mask his rebellion.

35:19.400 --> 35:21.040
Mr. Xie, do you imply

35:21.560 --> 35:23.640
that His Majesty should just sit and wait
for the enemy to besiege the Capital?

35:23.720 --> 35:25.120
Fifty thousand troops

35:25.920 --> 35:27.640
are the entire strength
of the Capital's garrison.

35:28.240 --> 35:30.600
Allowing these troops to enter the city?

35:30.680 --> 35:33.760
Do you understand the consequences
if things spin out of control?

35:35.040 --> 35:35.880
The Prince of Xiaonan Prefecture

35:35.960 --> 35:37.400
neither offered his condolences
nor paid his respects at court.

35:38.000 --> 35:39.320
His intentions could not be clearer.

35:39.920 --> 35:41.360
Now that Chu Ling is dead,

35:42.200 --> 35:43.920
the threat from the Northern Desert
is greater than ever.

35:44.960 --> 35:49.360
I fear the Prince
wants to take advantage of the chaos.

35:50.040 --> 35:52.280
Just as Mr. Xie said,

35:52.360 --> 35:53.840
the threat from the Northern Desert
is so massive

35:53.920 --> 35:55.600
that we cannot afford to gamble at all.

35:56.200 --> 35:57.760
If we are paranoid at this moment,

35:57.840 --> 35:59.160
and the Northern Desert truly breaks
through Yunzhong,

35:59.240 --> 36:02.320
the Capital will fall,
the state will no longer be a state,

36:02.960 --> 36:04.760
and we will be condemned for eternity.

36:04.840 --> 36:06.840
Your entire premise

36:07.360 --> 36:08.840
rests on the authenticity
of that military report.

36:10.080 --> 36:11.280
However, as I see it,

36:11.920 --> 36:14.800
the credibility of this military report
is still open to question.

36:15.920 --> 36:17.640
You took

36:18.400 --> 36:20.720
the frontier troops' victory reports
at face value

36:20.800 --> 36:22.840
and rewarded Yunzhong Prefecture.

36:22.920 --> 36:26.000
So dispatch riders bearing good news
are trustworthy,

36:26.520 --> 36:28.600
but those bringing ill tidings
are suddenly spies?

36:29.600 --> 36:30.680
What should we do then?

36:32.280 --> 36:33.160
Mr. Deng.

36:34.240 --> 36:35.120
I shall issue a decree

36:35.800 --> 36:37.120
ordering the Prince
of Xiaonan Prefecture's troops

36:37.200 --> 36:38.400
to be divided and stationed

36:38.480 --> 36:40.520
alongside the Capital's garrison
to defend the city.

36:41.360 --> 36:44.520
Your Majesty, this is indeed
an effective stalling tactic.

36:45.240 --> 36:48.000
Since the Prince and his heir use
the pretext of defending the Capital,

36:48.080 --> 36:50.480
Your Majesty can let them do so,

36:50.560 --> 36:52.680
but they must follow the deployments
of the imperial court.

36:53.320 --> 36:56.200
If they refuse to comply,
they will be treated as treacherous rebels

36:56.720 --> 36:58.000
whom anyone has the right to execute.

36:58.600 --> 37:02.200
When the state is in turmoil,
trouble will come from all sides.

37:02.800 --> 37:04.120
The Northern Desert King

37:04.640 --> 37:06.680
and the Prince of Xiaonan Prefecture
are no different.

37:07.760 --> 37:10.840
I have faced deat and weathered upheaval.

37:10.920 --> 37:15.520
I believe the State of Chu will endure.

37:16.120 --> 37:19.440
-We shall give our last breath
-We shall give our last breath

37:19.520 --> 37:22.680
-in service to Your Majesty
-in service to Your Majesty

37:22.760 --> 37:25.280
-and the State of Chu.
-and the State of Chu.

37:35.360 --> 37:36.600
You may withdraw.

37:40.920 --> 37:43.720
Mr. Xie, Mr. Deng,
what is it that you wish to tell me?

37:43.800 --> 37:46.160
-Your Majesty.
-The Prince of Xiaonan Prefecture leads

37:46.240 --> 37:47.080
not 50,000 troops,

37:47.160 --> 37:48.440
but 100,000.

37:48.960 --> 37:52.000
They are now less
than 800 li from the Capital.

37:53.400 --> 37:54.560
A military march to defend the Capital?

37:55.520 --> 37:56.840
No. This is treason.

37:56.920 --> 37:58.200
Mr. Xie, watch your words.

37:58.800 --> 38:00.800
We do not know
if the news is true or false,

38:01.320 --> 38:02.480
so we must not make rash judgments.

38:03.080 --> 38:04.680
Have you notified Zhao?

38:05.640 --> 38:08.040
I fear the news might be blocked
from reaching Her Highness.

38:08.120 --> 38:09.520
You keep claiming

38:09.600 --> 38:11.520
that the Prince of Xiaonan
and Xiao Xun are rebelling,

38:11.600 --> 38:13.240
yet you cannot produce
any concrete evidence.

38:14.160 --> 38:15.760
With the enemy closing in,

38:16.560 --> 38:17.960
the defense of the Capital
is our top priority.

38:18.040 --> 38:22.280
So you still wish to open the gates

38:22.920 --> 38:25.040
and let the Xiaonan Army in?

38:26.280 --> 38:28.640
I am doing this
for the safety of the Capital.

38:29.400 --> 38:31.200
If the Northern Desert launches an attack,

38:31.280 --> 38:32.880
how are the citizens
of the Capital supposed

38:32.960 --> 38:33.880
to protect themselves?

38:37.280 --> 38:38.560
Speculation is useless.

38:39.440 --> 38:43.880
We might as well wait and see
what Xiao Xun decides.

38:50.920 --> 38:52.240
I shall take my leave.

39:01.160 --> 39:02.880
This is the token
of the Imperial Guard Commander.

39:02.960 --> 39:04.600
After Uncle Yanlai left the Capital,

39:04.680 --> 39:06.360
the command of the Imperial Guard
was handed to his deputy.

39:07.280 --> 39:09.920
The token has been kept with me.

39:10.840 --> 39:14.400
Since the situation is critical,
I will leave it in your safekeeping.

39:18.000 --> 39:18.880
Very well.

39:20.000 --> 39:23.800
I will ensure your safety.

39:26.560 --> 39:28.280
His Majesty handed the token
of the Imperial Guard Commander over

39:28.360 --> 39:30.000
to Xie Yanfang.

39:30.080 --> 39:32.000
So the Prince of Xiaonan Prefecture
actually did him a favor?

39:32.880 --> 39:33.880
It was bound to happen sooner or later.

39:34.520 --> 39:38.160
Even without the Prince,
Mr. Xie would achieve his wish very soon.

39:39.000 --> 39:40.440
His Majesty is helpless.

39:40.960 --> 39:43.040
Why would he ever grow distant
from his uncle?

39:44.000 --> 39:46.400
A child's face and heart
are the most fickle things

39:46.920 --> 39:48.920
in the world.

39:49.800 --> 39:50.760
I warned him.

39:53.760 --> 39:55.040
No matter.

39:55.680 --> 40:00.080
Whoever His Majesty chooses to favor
is no concern of mine.

40:00.840 --> 40:03.520
Dispatch the edict to the Prince
of Xiaonan Prefecture at once.

40:05.640 --> 40:07.480
Select a suitable envoy to deliver it,

40:08.200 --> 40:09.960
and make sure it is done
with great fanfare.

40:11.000 --> 40:11.920
Understood.

40:12.000 --> 40:14.160
MEMORIAL ON EDUCATION AND AGRICULTURE

40:16.480 --> 40:18.520
Mr. Xie, a scout reports

40:18.600 --> 40:19.880
that the vanguard of Prince of Xiaonan
has arrived at Baili Pavilion.

40:26.520 --> 40:28.760
Xiao Xun used fake dispatch riders
to spread the news,

40:30.360 --> 40:33.000
executing a real palace coup under
the pretext of defending the Capital.

40:33.840 --> 40:35.840
The public has been taken in by him

40:35.920 --> 40:38.720
and truly believes he came
to protect His Majesty.

40:39.480 --> 40:41.440
They can't wait to throw wide
the city gates

40:42.200 --> 40:43.560
and welcome him with open arms.

40:43.640 --> 40:44.480
Deng Yi

40:45.120 --> 40:48.000
has clearly been won over by Xiao Xun
and is willing to do his bidding.

40:49.240 --> 40:50.400
Public opinion is like the wind.

40:51.480 --> 40:52.520
Fight it and you suffer.

40:52.600 --> 40:53.720
Ride it and you prevail.

40:55.040 --> 40:59.040
He can take the Capital
without spilling a drop of blood.

40:59.640 --> 41:00.920
What should we do?

41:01.000 --> 41:04.280
I have informed Yu
about the movements of the Xiaonan Army

41:04.920 --> 41:08.120
and coached him on what to say
and how to draft the imperial edict.

41:08.920 --> 41:11.280
It was all to fan the flames

41:12.000 --> 41:16.080
and let the coming battle play out
before the world.

41:17.120 --> 41:18.720
The Xie Family

41:20.240 --> 41:24.320
will be the greatest beneficiary
of this confrontation.

41:30.320 --> 41:31.800
Deng Yi had the way cleared with drums.

41:32.400 --> 41:33.680
The imperial envoy is heading
toward the Xiaonan Army Camp,

41:33.760 --> 41:34.600
the imperial banner held high.

41:37.800 --> 41:40.200
XIAONAN ARMY CAMP

41:41.000 --> 41:42.560
Any who neglect their duty

41:42.640 --> 41:44.960
shall face the full severity
of the military law.

41:45.040 --> 41:47.800
But those who stand resolute,
who defend this city with valor,

41:47.880 --> 41:49.480
shall be richly rewarded.

41:49.560 --> 41:54.440
So long as this city stands secure,
the state shall endure.

41:56.520 --> 41:58.120
Your Highness, please receive
the imperial edict.

42:02.840 --> 42:06.400
Your Highness, this is written
by His Majesty's own hand.

42:08.280 --> 42:09.280
I know.

42:09.360 --> 42:11.160
You… How insolent!

42:13.000 --> 42:13.880
Xiao Xun,

42:13.960 --> 42:16.960
are you and your father truly going
to defy the imperial command

42:17.040 --> 42:18.800
and commit treason?

42:25.960 --> 42:26.960
Imperial command?

42:29.520 --> 42:30.720
Treason?

42:33.480 --> 42:35.120
The edict states

42:35.640 --> 42:39.000
that 50,000 troops
stand arrayed outside the city.

42:39.680 --> 42:42.960
Aren't they just waiting for me
to defy the command?

42:44.000 --> 42:48.800
It is the perfect pretext
to have me branded a rebel

42:48.880 --> 42:49.720
and start a war.

42:52.800 --> 42:58.560
When blades are drawn
and the cavalry cuts through,

42:59.720 --> 43:01.720
the dead will be beyond count

43:01.800 --> 43:03.440
and the land strewn with the starving.

43:04.600 --> 43:07.080
All of it will become
the fault of Xiaonan Prefecture.

43:08.440 --> 43:12.880
And with the false charge of treason
you have already pinned on me,

43:13.680 --> 43:15.040
the crimes only pile higher.

43:16.440 --> 43:20.440
And I would be guilty
beyond all redemption.

43:27.040 --> 43:28.360
I accept the edict

43:29.000 --> 43:33.280
and will heed His Majesty's command
to protect the Capital.

43:33.880 --> 43:35.000
But sir,

43:35.600 --> 43:37.280
casting an imperial edict into the fire

43:38.080 --> 43:39.600
is an unpardonable offense
against His Majesty.

43:43.280 --> 43:44.240
How dare you!

43:44.840 --> 43:47.480
Go. Make sure he is "taken care of".

43:49.120 --> 43:50.160
Xiao Xun,

43:50.840 --> 43:52.320
you're persecuting a loyal minister!

43:52.400 --> 43:53.640
You will meet a miserable end!

43:53.720 --> 43:57.000
Xiao Xun, how dare you
burn the imperial decree?

44:00.000 --> 44:01.240
Hear my command.

44:02.160 --> 44:03.360
Break camp tomorrow.

44:03.440 --> 44:07.040
Split our forces into four routes
and advance on the Capital!

44:07.920 --> 44:09.080
-Understood!
-Understood!

44:09.160 --> 44:10.600
THE CAPITAL
